    <string name="termux_wizard_step_install_title">Install Termux</string>
    <string name="termux_wizard_step_install_body">Termux is a free Linux terminal app. The AI Keyboard runs the Claude and Gemini command-line tools inside it locally on your phone — your queries and OAuth tokens never leave the device. Install Termux from F-Droid (the Play Store version is unmaintained).</string>
